# Containers

Once the fit of the system in the overall landscape is understood it useful to zoom in to the system boundary.

![Containers](images/Containers.png)

This diagram shows how the Academy Transfers service does not store any data on the projects being worked up - this responsibility is delegated to the Academies API, which is managed by a separate team.

The Academy Transfers service utilizes Redis as a session store, allowing for horizontal scalability and stateless application containers.

